In this article, President Joseph R. Biden Jr. emphasizes the importance of mentorship and recognizes January 2022 as National Mentoring Month. He highlights the role that mentors play in guiding and empowering young people to reach their full potential. The Biden administration is investing in programs that provide mentorship, counseling, and employment services to support the next generation. President Biden calls upon Americans to celebrate National Mentoring Month through mentoring activities and programs.